<section id="slr_sizeInfoRef">
  <title>slr_sizeInfoRef</title>
  <para>This <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>string
    property<?oxy_custom_end?> is used to point to data that provide the same function as the <olink
      targetdoc="size-info.xml" targetptr="slr_size_info"><code>skr_sizeInfo</code></olink>
    <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>string
    property<?oxy_custom_end?> does, but with the data stored outside the inline content of the
    JLIFF segment. This attribute is only allowed on the <olink
      targetdoc="../../elements/inline/ec.xml" targetptr="ec"><code>ec</code></olink> element if
    that element has the <olink targetdoc="../attributes/isolated.xml" targetptr="isolated"
        ><code>isolated</code></olink> attribute set to <code>"yes"</code>. Otherwise the
    <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>string
    property<?oxy_custom_end?> on the paired <olink targetdoc="../../elements/inline/sc.xml"
      targetptr="sc"><code>sc</code></olink> element also cover its partner <olink
      targetdoc="../../elements/inline/ec.xml" targetptr="ec"><code>ec</code></olink>
    element.</para>
  <para><?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?><emphasis>Type:</emphasis>
    string.</para><?oxy_custom_end?>
  <para><emphasis>Value description:</emphasis>
    <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="140,255,140"?>NMTOKEN: a string matching
    the pattern <code>[-._:A-Za-z0-9]+</code><?oxy_custom_end?>, a reference to data that provide
    the same information that could be otherwise put in a <olink targetdoc="size-info.xml"
      targetptr="slr_size_info"><code>slr_sizeInfo</code></olink>
    <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>string
    property<?oxy_custom_end?>. The reference <glossterm>must</glossterm> point to an
    <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>object<?oxy_custom_end?> in a
      <olink targetdoc="../../elements/size_restriction/data.xml" targetptr="slr_data"
        ><code>slr_data</code></olink> object that is a sibling to the
    <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>object<?oxy_custom_end?> this
    <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>string
    property<?oxy_custom_end?> is attached to or a sibling to one of its ancestors. </para>
  <para><emphasis>Default value:</emphasis> undefined.</para>
  <para><emphasis>Used in:</emphasis>
    <olink targetdoc="../../elements/structural/file.xml" targetptr="file"
    ><code>file</code></olink>, <olink targetdoc="../../elements/structural/group.xml"
      targetptr="group"><code>group</code></olink>, <olink
      targetdoc="../../elements/structural/unit.xml" targetptr="unit"><code>unit</code></olink>,
      <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,64,0"?><olink
      targetdoc="../../elements/inline/pc.xml" targetptr="pc"><code>pc</code></olink>,
      <?oxy_custom_end?><olink targetdoc="../../elements/inline/sc.xml" targetptr="sc"
        ><code>sc</code></olink>, <olink targetdoc="../../elements/inline/ec.xml" targetptr="ec"
        ><code>ec</code></olink>, and <olink targetdoc="../../elements/inline/ph.xml" targetptr="ph"
        ><code>ph</code></olink>, </para>
  <itemizedlist>
    <title>Constraints</title>
    <listitem>
      <para>This <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>string property<?oxy_custom_end?>
        <glossterm>must not</glossterm> be specified if and only if <olink targetdoc="size-info.xml"
          targetptr="slr_size_info"><code>slr_sizeInfo</code></olink> is used. They <glossterm>must
          not</glossterm> be specified at the same time.</para>
    </listitem>
  </itemizedlist>
</section>
